{"tid":2282902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] [長文分析] 侵要翻盤嘅可能性","createTime":"2020-11-12T07:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T14:36:13.000Z","uid":198088,"like":193,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"3b2bbabc77927045ebd17ea1cc28bd36fcf65c71","tid":2282902,"uid":198088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"有個傻仔開左呢個post, 但乜分析都冇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2282754/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2282754/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n咁我咪開多個話俾大家知而家咩情況囉，順便串下個傻仔:<br />\n<br />\n侵而家有232票, WI GA 重點加audit, 應該拎到, 加埋都258 票。<br />\n<br />\n剩番<br />\nMI 16<br />\nPA 20<br />\nNV 6<br />\nAZ 11<br />\n<br />\nAZ 目前應該反cup 唔到，就算反cup 左對大局冇咩影響，因為得11票, 只可以做到269: 269。如果要連任點都要加多個州<br />\n<br />\n反而如果主攻PA 或者MI (目前睇到都係咁), 只要只中一個反cup 就可以258 + 16/ 20, 去到274 / 278 票。而且trump 而家開始打軟件出cheat呢個point，目前間軟件公司嘅有員工做左金手指(未公開)，<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RyanAFournier/status/1326570630234447872?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRyanAFournier%2Fstatus%2F1326570630234447872%3Fs%3D20&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Aux3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=05a4cec7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRyanAFournier%2Fstatus%2F1326570630234447872%3Fs%3D20&h=0e3bd066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RyanAFournier/status/1326570630234447872?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n加上第二個USPS 員都出左來做金手指（搵左同一間媒體爆料）<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JamesOKeefeIII/status/1326723900642824198?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJamesOKeefeIII%2Fstatus%2F1326723900642824198%3Fs%3D20&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Aux3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=8384dfcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJamesOKeefeIII%2Fstatus%2F1326723900642824198%3Fs%3D20&h=601c433d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JamesOKeefeIII/status/1326723900642824198?s=20</a> <br />\n<br />